Description: 2014 Clapton Strat, Pewter. Played rarely but maintained. Sat in its case for most of the nearly 5 years I had it. I don't think I ever installed the bar, which is in the bag with all the case candy. I did put Fender/Schaller strap locks on it. Straight, frets great, everything works. No rash in the back. Some surface swirl back by trem back behind where your hand would sit. I couldn't get it to show in the pics, juist being honest. Comes with the Fender Case and all candy. Plays great and sounds like what it is. Will ship within 48 hours via UPS once payment clears Paypal to my account. USA Lower 48 only.
